---
/**
 * About — the verbatim positioning paragraph plus a flagged placeholder line
 * for personal interests (not invented). Asymmetric: a mono side-label column
 * and the prose column.
 */
---

<div class="about" data-reveal-group="about">
  <div class="about__aside" data-reveal>
    <p class="about__label">Abstract</p>
    <p class="about__note">
      The thread: figure out exactly how a system works, then build the thing
      that should exist.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="about__prose" data-reveal>
    <p class="about__lead">
      I study electrical engineering and artificial intelligence at the
      University of Pennsylvania. My research is in biophysics: I build
      mathematical models of how DNA nanoswitches change shape and bind, work
      that has fed into a drug-discovery platform now developing therapeutics. I
      also build things that move and learn, like a robotic arm I trained with
      imitation learning. The thread across all of it is figuring out exactly
      how a system works, then building the thing that should exist.
    </p>

    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: one or two sentences of personal interests outside the
         lab, in Luc's own voice. Not invented; rendered as a flagged note. -->
    <p class="about__placeholder">
      [PLACEHOLDER: one or two sentences of personal interests outside the lab,
      in Luc's own voice.]
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(10rem, 14rem) 1fr;
    gap: clamp(var(--space-5), 4vw, var(--space-8));
  }

  .about__aside {
    border-top: var(--border-strong);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
  }
  .about__label {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--c-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-mono-label);
    letter-spacing: var(--ls-label);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .about__note {
    color: var(--c-text-faint);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: var(--lh-mono);
  }

  .about__prose {
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
  .about__lead {
    font-size: var(--fs-body-l);
    color: var(--c-text);
  }
  .about__placeholder {
    margin-top: var(--space-5);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border: 1px dashed var(--c-hairline-strong);
    border-radius: var(--r-md);
    color: var(--c-text-faint);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-5);
    }
  }
</style>
